metadata.name: Monochrome Mood
metadata.description:
Afternoon light illuminates the misty, coastal air over the jungles of the Mentawai Islands, Indonesia. This image is a study of contrasts. The dense island vegetation gives way to the expansive Indian Ocean while the brightness of equatorial sun is hidden in the shadows of the canopy.  

This image was captured on Pulau Nyang-Nyang in the Mentawai Islands, Indonesia. 
275mm f10 1/1250sec
